## Generate Authentication URL

### Description
Redirect users to this URL to grant your application permissions (scopes) to access Google APIs on their behalf.

### Method
GET

### Endpoint
`/auth/url` (Conceptual endpoint for URL generation)

### Parameters
#### Query Parameters
- **access_type** (string) - Optional - Specifies the access type, e.g., 'offline' to get a refresh token.
